attributionInfo.brokerName: Berkshire Hathaway Home Services Professional Realty

data.description: The Perfect Ranch Style Home in Mature Section of Triple Crown! Featuring 3 bedrooms & 2 full bathrooms. Kitchen boasts granite tops, island, pantry, hardwood floors. Walkout to your screened porch and enjoy a peaceful, landscaped setting. Spacious great room with soaring ceilings, brick fireplace & wet bar adding a touch of luxury. Primary bedroom suite features walk-in closet & private bath w/ double vanity, tiled shower. Huge lower level with walk-out. Move-in ready, freshly painted, updated flooring, updated lighting. Desirable Mann/Gray/Ryle district. Welcome to your new home!
